<title>BELGIUM: Dr Solomon's prices offer.</title>
<headline>Dr Solomon's prices offer.</headline>
<dateline>BRUSSELS 1997-06-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>British computer anti-virus software makers Dr Solomon's Group Plc said on Friday its secondary offering of American Depositary Shares (ADS) on Nasdaq and Easdaq had been priced at $22.625 per ADS.</p>
<p>Dr Solomon's said it had sold a total of 4,169,215 ADS via private placements in the U.S. and Europe. The offering lifts Dr Solomon's free float of shares on Nasdaq and Easdaq to 54 percent.</p>
<p>-- Nick Antonovics, Brussels Newsroom +32 2 287 6817, Fax +32 2 230 7710</p>
